  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cyber Protocol is a fast-paced, retro-inspired arcade puzzle game wrapped in a neon-lit cyberpunk aesthetic. Featuring dynamic gameplay and energetic music, it puts both your logic and reflexes to the test. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready for the challenge? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285010/extras/378fb428f1b7c016ba925942536d4f34.avif?t=1772624271\" width=1560 height=146 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285010/extras/99ae7d765050d959a3f60ace4dcab796.poster.avif?t=1772624271\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285010/extras/99ae7d765050d959a3f60ace4dcab796.webm?t=1772624271\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285010/extras/99ae7d765050d959a3f60ace4dcab796.mp4?t=1772624271\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast, challenging, and addictive gameplay. Careful planning is essential alongside quick, reflexive thinking. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285010/extras/bea3a945a31383f6caea029975448fab.avif?t=1772624271\" width=1560 height=146 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285010/extras/292466af0d92fddecbd404774c86ea44.poster.avif?t=1772624271\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285010/extras/292466af0d92fddecbd404774c86ea44.webm?t=1772624271\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285010/extras/292466af0d92fddecbd404774c86ea44.mp4?t=1772624271\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Progress through 100 handcrafted levels that each introduce fresh and original puzzles. New layouts, obstacles, and traps with unique mechanics ensure that no two challenges feel the same.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285010/extras/1b69d29362977168b5e54f35b3654dc3.avif?t=1772624271\" width=1560 height=146 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285010/extras/4d28a6f6de928630b9e562cc8976862c.poster.avif?t=1772624271\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285010/extras/4d28a6f6de928630b9e562cc8976862c.webm?t=1772624271\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285010/extras/4d28a6f6de928630b9e562cc8976862c.mp4?t=1772624271\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle against a ruthless hivemind in solo mode. Or invite friends and family to PvP splitscreen challenges for up four players to try lay claim to the title of the ultimate hacker     </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285010/extras/d13b287845522b34a48198fc542ed1db.avif?t=1772624271\" width=1560 height=146 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285010/extras/1a1ae2126c209d2cdf62d2cc2d5c8b1e.poster.avif?t=1772624271\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285010/extras/1a1ae2126c209d2cdf62d2cc2d5c8b1e.webm?t=1772624271\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285010/extras/1a1ae2126c209d2cdf62d2cc2d5c8b1e.mp4?t=1772624271\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Craving more of a challenge? Try hacking the system in Arcade Mode, where the pace gets faster, and lives are limited. The challenge is brutal, but the most skilled players can earn a spot in the global Top 20 hacker ranking leaderboards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285010/extras/15419fdaa45f806241b989b6d12c1510.avif?t=1772624271\" width=1560 height=146 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285010/extras/5cffa261ba87d06f20c515f99032451d.poster.avif?t=1772624271\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285010/extras/5cffa261ba87d06f20c515f99032451d.webm?t=1772624271\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285010/extras/5cffa261ba87d06f20c515f99032451d.mp4?t=1772624271\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you’re missing the classic retro era, <strong>Cyber Protocol</strong> has got you covered. Unlock various additional visual and musical themes to find your perfect ‘80s arcade experience  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285010/extras/a771a942ba70373e584147a9e356d18b.avif?t=1772624271\" width=1560 height=146 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285010/extras/69429a8d94867d6f08e00925ee490c0e.poster.avif?t=1772624271\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285010/extras/69429a8d94867d6f08e00925ee490c0e.webm?t=1772624271\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285010/extras/69429a8d94867d6f08e00925ee490c0e.mp4?t=1772624271\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sit back and immerse yourself in Cyber Protocol’s pulsating 8-bit synthwave soundtrack, perfectly tuned to keep your adrenaline high.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1285010/extras/faf1528ef558eaeb8063ca067675a0f7.avif?t=1772624271\" width=1560 height=146 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100 handcrafted levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Various puzzles and challenges</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast-paced gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Singleplayer mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Additional split-screen PvP challenges for up to 4 players</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Global leaderboard challenges</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stunning soundtrack</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An additional 5 visual and 3 musical themes to unlock</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >24 achievements </p></li></ul>",
